data.description: This remarkable 3-bedroom (4th bedroom den) residence nestled in the Eastmark Community is the one you've been waiting for! Explore inside to find yourself in a bright open layout featuring tile flooring, fresh soothing palette, & modern recessed lighting. The beautiful kitchen is ready for you to improve your cooking skills showcasing white shaker cabinets adorned with crown moulding, stylish tile backsplash, quartz counters, black stainless steel appliances, a walk-in pantry, & a large central island including a breakfast bar. The primary bedroom boasts soft carpet throughout, an immaculate ensuite with dual sinks, & a walk-in closet. Fall in love with the charming backyard offering the perfect space for outdoor breakfast or simply relaxing with a good book! Don't miss out!
